#: ../../docs/classes/class_generic6dofjoint.rst:14
msgid ""
"The generic 6-degrees-of-freedom joint can implement a variety of joint "
"types by locking certain axes' rotation or translation."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/classes/class_generic6dofjoint.rst:17
msgid "Description"
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/classes/class_generic6dofjoint.rst:19
msgid ""
"The first 3 DOF axes are linear axes, which represent translation of "
"Bodies, and the latter 3 DOF axes represent the angular motion. Each axis"
" can be either locked, or limited."
msgstr ""

